  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 3rd level, you begin to become familiar with your ghastly jutsu and how it interacts with the world around you. </p><p>You gain proficiency in Illusions, Insight, and Stealth if you are not already. </p><p>When you would make an Ability check using Stealth, you can use Wisdom in place of Dexterity. </p><p>Additionally, when you would make a Stealth check using Dexterity or Wisdom, you can spend one superiority dice adding it to your checks result.</p>",
